{"tid":658670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府擬增「特快專線」輸入人才　料較多來自中國","createTime":"2018-05-09T07:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T04:56:14.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c0c2d000b420d2f1ba06dd2d8353c3783ae4fec1","tid":658670,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T07:33:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%93%AC%E5%A2%9E-%E7%89%B9%E5%BF%AB%E5%B0%88%E7%B7%9A-%E8%BC%B8%E5%85%A5%E5%89%B5%E7%A7%91%E5%B0%88%E6%89%8D-%E6%96%99%E8%BC%83%E5%A4%9A%E5%85%A7%E8%87%AA%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%25B3%25B6-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%25A2%259E-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E5%25B0%2588%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%2589%25B5%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%2589%258D-%25E6%2596%2599%25E8%25BC%2583%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%2F&d=tXfh0r%2FUpTK3OaQPDnQbRwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=d2acf50e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%25B3%25B6-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%25A2%259E-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E5%25B0%2588%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%2589%25B5%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%2589%258D-%25E6%2596%2599%25E8%25BC%2583%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%2F&h=71e3ddc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%93%AC%E5%A2%9E-%E7%89%B9%E5%BF%AB%E5%B0%88%E7%B7%9A-%E8%BC%B8%E5%85%A5%E5%89%B5%E7%A7%91%E5%B0%88%E6%89%8D-%E6%96%99%E8%BC%83%E5%A4%9A%E5%85%A7%E8%87%AA%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E589B5E696B0E58F8AE7A791E68A80E5B180E5B180E995B7E6A58AE58189E99B84_hRvsI_1200x0.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE589B5E696B0E58F8AE7A791E68A80E5B180E5B180E995B7E6A58AE58189E99B84_hRvsI_1200x0.PNG&h=e57a2e05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《星島日報》頭版報道，創新科技局、保安局及入境處會合作，最快在今年暑假推出「特快專線」輸入創科專才計劃。有業界人士表示，曾有聞這安排，並指措施應是配合河套科學園區發展。<br />\n<br />\n報道又引述消息估計，現時內地創科發展一日千里、速度驚人，擁有較多相關人才，初步推算新的創科專才計畫，會吸引較多內地人才。<br />\n<br />\n按入境處「一般就業政策」，最快4星期可完成工作簽證，但新專責小組將加快處理創科專才申請，讓批核時間少於四星期。創科專才如成功逗留本港滿7年，可申請居留權。"},{"pid":"c3bac572bcc04ff9e0afe3768fc2110dc3aa0aca","tid":658670,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T07:41:43.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"dc9745b29583312b5600712c86ee59b0136bc3e1","tid":658670,"uid":108090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T07:47:11.000Z","msg":"習帝萬歲"},{"pid":"5ea710890c6060b76890b2c55cf713f6d7596ec1","tid":658670,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:24:35.000Z","msg":"thank you government"},{"pid":"f79e7b5ccb81187e367e3ecce30b29dfd9b9fabf","tid":658670,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76280177dcbbbd6a9753e8e712e063a18275fd7","tid":658670,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T03:18:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5b9e7c836a181ab4606992562b6d0a54b57a9f","tid":658670,"uid":1221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T03:24:54.000Z","msg":"賣港不遺餘力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea1e75f0e9a1632e6f6ff44e29d4579467c9a8f","tid":658670,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T03:25:54.000Z","msg":"殖民地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad19e9e7b058bce0bdb447